    <text type="letter">
        <body>
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <name type="place">328 Mickle st&#8212;Camden<ptr target="nyp.00544_n1"
                    />&#8212;</name>
                    <date when="1886-03-26" rend="right">March 26</date>
                </dateline>
            </opener>    
            <p>Am ab't the same as usual&#8212;Had a bad spell two weeks ago, but am now around
                after my sort, nearly the same (a letting down a little peg, if no more, every
                time)&#8212;Yes I have had superb treatment from my English friends&#8212;Yours of
                23[?]d rec'd<ptr target="nyp.00544_n2"/>&#8212;I dont know whether I told you that a
                young Englishman who came into a fortune not long since, sent me 50 pounds<ptr
                    target="nyp.00544_n3"/>&#8212;then the <hi rend="italic">Nineteenth Cent</hi>
                paid me 30&#163; for the little poem<ptr target="nyp.00544_n4"/>&#8212;</p>
            <closer>
                <signed>W W</signed>
            </closer>
        </body>
